Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:09.76,sign_31763_303_Strelizia_Apath,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fs40\fsp20\pos(1292,903)}鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:13.20,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭拒絕了一切的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:16.27,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,也就是說她幹掉了我們的程序？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:22.77,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在我感覺你比何時都離我更近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:26.61,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你所想的事情　我都能清清楚楚地明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:30.20,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從今以後　無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.45,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的心永遠在一起　Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:58.93,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,看到了　我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:02.27,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,啊　多麼美麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:04.27,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,我的天燕座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:08.03,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭·天燕座！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:17.12,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.30,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,由叫龍製成的生命之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:24.67,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,雖說我們想要的不止這些　但我們就先這樣暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:36.18,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,但是我們會再次來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:40.18,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,那時候我們會帶著全部兵力{Flag}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.19,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,將這顆星球消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:44.29,Default,9a,0,0,0,,爸爸...
